<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>결제 영수증</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .receipt {
      background: white;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .header p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .label {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .value {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .total {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .total .value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #0064ff;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="receipt">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>결제 영수증</h1>
      <p><%= provider %> Mock</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">결제 키</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.paymentKey %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">주문번호</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.orderId %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">상품명</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.orderName %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">결제수단</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.method || '-' %></span>
    </div>
    <% if (payment.cardCompany) { %>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">카드사</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.cardCompany %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">카드번호</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.cardNumber %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">승인번호</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.approveNo %></span>
    </div>
    <% } %>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="label">결제일시</span>
      <span class="value"><%= payment.approvedAt || payment.createdAt %></span>
    </div>

    <div class="total">
      <div class="row">
        <span class="label">결제금액</span>
        <span class="value"><%= payment.amount.toLocaleString() %>원</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>이 영수증은 Mock PG Server에서 발행되었습니다.</p>
      <p>실제 결제가 이루어지지 않았습니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
